author: SciShow
description:
See if the ACT could be the right test for you at https://www.act.org/SciShow 

Silfra Fissue in Iceland is a remarkable place where the Earth is tearing itself apart. Here, intrepid divers can reach out and touch two continents at once. But... should they?

Hosted by: Reid Reimers (he/him)
